      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUNK YARD HIPPY (4) charged out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but swamped late when a close up sixth (17.60) at this track over 300m. Rates on top in this line up. LADY FREYA (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 3.5 lengths fifth (17.56) but back to the course now of her latest success. Has a good record here at this journey. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. FLETCHER KEEPING (8) was narrowly beaten when placing two back but missed the frame latest finishing fourth (23.02) in a Grade 5 at this track. Can feature with the right run. BLUEY BRANN (6) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
